The president of the state affairs is the ultimate decisionmaker in regards to North Korea's nuclear arsenal. The position is held by the
WPK general secretary
and serves as the
supreme leader of North Korea
.
[
74
]
Israel
Prime Minister of Israel
Requires agreement of the
Minister of Defense
and
